<subSubSection id="18A57B080D9C263DDD3D9754C4CA6146" pageId="0" pageNumber="84104" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph id="275FDDE4C4724958079DD84E345A8DA5" pageId="0" pageNumber="84104">Diagnosis</paragraph>
<paragraph id="1EE0317E15E49DF24EE25600AA668B95" pageId="0" pageNumber="84104">
Amongst the seven genera (
<taxonomicName id="5639B0E79F7624AEC009C782BDAB6C3F" authorityName="Dejean" authorityYear="1828" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Trigonotoma" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Trigonotoma" order="Coleoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="84104" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="5B90CFD4003272E8A1AC82830CD6E2FA" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="84104">Trigonotoma</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
Dejean, 
<taxonomicName id="061C2B11F3534C404FA2D5292463EE7A" authorityName="Dejean" authorityYear="1828" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Lesticus" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Lesticus" order="Coleoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="84104" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="5B674CD2CC42DEBA74A6FB5B858C8ACB" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="84104">Lesticus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
Dejean, 
<taxonomicName id="45B5CFA0EB46EEF28A52D3B18EAC8BC5" authorityName="Bates" authorityYear="1892" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Euryaptus" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Euryaptus" order="Coleoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="84104" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="BAB4BE3F606920EAD4CC5B04273A7B9F" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="84104">Euryaptus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
Bates, 
<taxonomicName id="343799DA6F06719C4CD660BF79526158" authorityName="Andrewes" authorityYear="1939" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Nesites" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Nesites" order="Coleoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="84104" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="C11C43748ABF0A5DFD544AE43E58A66C" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="84104">Nesites</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
Andrews, 
<taxonomicName id="35BA0C774DA3AAEDE014C9FA2BEE0419" authorityName="Dubault, Lassalle &amp; Roux" authorityYear="2008" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Pareuryaptus" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Pareuryaptus" order="Coleoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="84104" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="54B6DA8D063A403EE273B6EC67240EDC" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="84104">Pareuryaptus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
Dubault, Lassalle &amp; Roux, 
<taxonomicName id="EE578F81FCF9620CB049FCE41DF1437C" authorityName="Roux &amp; Lassalle&amp;Dubault" authorityYear="2016" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Leiolesticus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Leiolesticus" order="Coleoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="84104" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="E786CC2B10D51F246E5A1865ACCCB594" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="84104">Leiolesticus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
Roux, Lassalle &amp; Dubault and 
<taxonomicName id="9F9D8562A05A78196D780EBABC1FF0C9" authorityName="Fedorenko" authorityYear="2020" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Trigonaptus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Trigonaptus" order="Coleoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="84104" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="BAE1493E0D875A26FE5EE38FCFDDDACE" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="84104">Trigonaptus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
Fedorenko) of 
<taxonomicName id="EFA418F9EC15EF64492FF29A2322764D" authorityName="Fedorenko" authorityYear="2020" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Trigonaptus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="" order="Coleoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="84104" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subTribe" subTribe="Trigonotomina">Trigonotomina</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="279899544048A9EBB83930AE512603CA" authorityName="Dubault, Lassalle &amp; Roux" authorityYear="2008" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Pareuryaptus" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Pareuryaptus" order="Coleoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="84104" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="A6154168990D9F7660B54A9BB1E52BC4" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="84104">Pareuryaptus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
can be distinguished by the following character combinations: first antennomere (scape) longer than the length of the second and third antennomeres combined; antennal pedicel glabrous, without ventral seta; apex of labrum emarginate, with six apical setae, four grouped near the middle, the lateral setae evidently distant from the median four ones; parascutellar striae absent or very short; metacoxa unisetose; females with one seta on each side of sternite VII (
<bibRefCitation id="D5634135BFD27EB67CAC5E2BBC8BA11B" author="Roux, P" journalOrPublisher="B. Lassalle et P. Roux, France" pageId="0" pageNumber="84104" refId="B7776349" refString="Roux, P, Lassalle, B, Dubault, G, 2016. Les Trigonotomi. Revision. B. Lassalle et P. Roux, France" title="Les Trigonotomi. Revision." year="2016">Roux et al. 2016</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="016190D0192A9F03D78D8820B7FE1D65" author="Fedorenko, D. N." journalOrPublisher="Russian Entomological Journal" pageId="0" pageNumber="84104" pagination="38 - 52" refId="B7858855" refString="Fedorenko, D. N., 2020. New taxa of Pterostichini (Coleoptera: Carabidae) from Vietnam. Russian Entomological Journal 29 (1): 38 - 52" title="New taxa of Pterostichini (Coleoptera: Carabidae) from Vietnam" volume="29" year="2020">Fedorenko 2020</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
